query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q tq s) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 5
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('access-token',
'caliburn.micro',
'heatmap',
'kinect',
'laravel-routing',
'mvp',
'opengraph',
'projection',
'qtp',
'text-editor',
'ubuntu-18.04',
'webpack-2');
